NHL Draft

Source: R/nhl_draft.R
nhl_draft.Rd

Returns information on draft

nhl_draft()

Value

Returns a data frame: * year - * round - * pick_overall - * pick_in_round - * team_id - * team_name - * team_link - * prospect_id - * prospect_full_name - * prospect_link -

  nhl_draft()
